E. Design, implement, maintain, and document safeguards that control the internal and 14 15 external risks to the security, confidentiality, or integrity of Nonpublic Personal Information 16 identified in response to sub-Provision VI.D. Each safeguard shall be based on the volume and 17 sensitivity of the Personal Information that is at risk, and the likelihood that the risk could be 18 realized and result in the unauthorized access, collection, use, alteration, destruction, or 19 disclosure of the Personal Information.

